A visualization of how the intervals $U_i=[a_i,b_i]$ are defined. If $f(i)$ lands inside $U_i$, then the next interval $U_{i+1}$ shrinks to exclude it. Try to predict what will happen in the next step and click "Advance" to check if you were right.
